ted in the <a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\">Code of Ethics<\\/a> have been identified will be rejected. <\\/span><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">Todos los manuscritos enviados a la <\\/span><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"> ser\\u00e1n revisados utilizando <\\/span><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">diversas herramientas de detecci\\u00f3n de plagio. Se rechazar\\u00e1n los art\\u00edculos en que se detecte plagio, auto-plagio, dudosa citaci\\u00f3n y las normas que indica el <a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/politicaseticasdepublicacion\\">C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/a> de la revista. <\\/span><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Plagiarism","es_ES":"Plagio"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"182","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"32","parentId":"24","seq":"7"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false}],"_data":{"id":"175","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"24","parentId":"0","seq":"0"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"33","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"comopublicar","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">: <\\/span><strong>Research Academic Journal <\\/strong><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\">is a triannual publication of scientific and humanistic resear