","es_ES":""},"title":{"en_US":"How to submit","es_ES":"\\u00bfC\\u00f3mo publicar?"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"35","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"criteriosyprocedimientoseditoriales","content":{"en_US":"<p style=\\"page-break-before: auto; page-break-after: auto;\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong>: <strong>Research Academic Journal <\\/strong>is a triannual publication of scientific and humanistic research, edited by the Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM. It publishes, in either Spanish or English, original articles, essays and reviews on the five academic fields formed in the institution, with the purposes of intensifying the sharing of academic discussion, contributing to the construction of basic and applied research, and promoting as well as disseminating its results in and out of Mexico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Fig\\u016bras is available online, in digital format, through XML and PDF open access files, looking forward to promoting research exchange.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Fig\\u016bras evokes the act of transforming, tracing and representing in each publication the findings that authors lay on their articles.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">The topics and research of the manuscripts must have high quality and originality. Manuscripts can be written in either Spanish or English covering topics of any of the following academic fields:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Architecture, Visual and Multimedia Communication<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanities and Arts<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Legal Sciences<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Mathematics and Engineering<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Social Sciences<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><strong><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/procedimientoeditorial\\">Publishing process<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/revisionabiertaporpares\\">Open Peer Review (OPR)<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/aceptacion\\">Acceptance<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n <\\/strong>es una publicaci\\u00f3n cuatrimestral de investigaci\\u00f3n cient\\u00edfica y human\\u00edstica editada por la Facultad de Estudios Superiores Acatl\\u00e1n-UNAM que publica, en espa\\u00f1ol o ingl\\u00e9s, art\\u00edculos originales, ensayos y rese\\u00f1as cr\\u00edticas en los cinco campos de conocimiento cultivados en la entidad, con los objetivos de intensificar la participaci\\u00f3n del di\\u00e1logo acad\\u00e9mico, contribuir en la configuraci\\u00f3n de la investigaci\\u00f3n b\\u00e1sica y aplicada y promover y difundir sus resultados en M\\u00e9xico y en el extranjero.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Fig\\u016bras se encuentra disponible en formato digital para su consulta en archivos de acceso abierto en formato XML y PDF con la finalidad de impulsar el intercambio de investigaciones.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Fig\\u016bras evoca la acci\\u00f3n de transformar, delinear y representar en cada una de sus publicaciones, los hallazgos que cada participante plasma en sus art\\u00edculos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Los temas e investigaciones de los art\\u00edculos deben ser originales y de profunda calidad en la investigaci\\u00f3n. Los art\\u00edculos pueden estar escritos en espa\\u00f1ol o ingl\\u00e9s y podr\\u00e1n abordar temas de cualquiera de los siguientes campos de conocimiento:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/arquitecturacomunicacionvisualmultimedia\\">Arquitectura, Comunicaci\\u00f3n Visual y Multimedia<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciasjuridicas\\">Ciencias jur\\u00eddicas<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/cienciassociales\\">Ciencias sociales<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/humanidadesyartes\\">Humanidades y Artes<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li class=\\"show\\" style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: 400;\\"><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/matematicaseingenieria\\">Matem\\u00e1ticas e Ingenier\\u00eda<\\/a><\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><strong><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/procedimientoeditorial\\">Procedimiento editorial<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><strong><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/revisionabiertaporpares\\">Revisi\\u00f3n abierta por pares (open peer review, OPR)<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><strong><a style=\\"color: #e26627;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/ojs\\/index.php\\/figuras\\/aceptacion\\">Aceptaci\\u00f3n<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Editorial criteria and procedures","es_ES":"Criterios y procedimientos editoriales"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"184","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"35","parentId":"33","seq":"9"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"36","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"opr","content":{"en_US":"<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">The type of review to be used is open peer review (OPR) from only one of the reviewers. This means that three reviewers will submit their evaluations of each of the manuscripts anonymously and, by an open computational procedure, one of them will be revealed in order to interact with the author, if necessary.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">In this way, the names of the authors and two of the reviewers are not disclosed and just one of the evaluations is known. Thus, this system keeps the integrity of open access and open data procedures, and provides certainty to the peer-reviewing process.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">Once the reviewers accept the procedure and the manuscript, they will examine it carefully according to their field of specialization and the publishing guidelines of <\\/span><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras. <\\/strong><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\">Then<\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">, they will send the opinion with either the acknowledgement (including suggestions for change) or the denial of its publication.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">El tipo de revisi\\u00f3n de los art\\u00edculos ser\\u00e1 por pares a revisi\\u00f3n abierta (open peer review, OPR) de uno de los tres dictaminadores; es decir, para cada art\\u00edculo habr\\u00e1 tres revisores que entregar\\u00e1n sus dict\\u00e1menes an\\u00f3nimamente y, por un proceso aleatorio computacional, se realizar\\u00e1 la apertura de una de las identidades de los revisores que podr\\u00e1 interactuar con el autor si \\u00e9ste lo solicita.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">De esta manera, los nombres de los autores y dos de los dictaminadores no ser\\u00e1n revelados y s\\u00f3lo una de las evaluaciones podr\\u00e1 ser conocida. Esta forma de revisi\\u00f3n mantiene el esp\\u00edritu de acceso abierto (Open Access) y datos abiertos (Open Data), y busca dar mayor certidumbre al sistema de arbitraje de revistas internacionales.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"western\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Una vez que los dictaminadores acepten el procedimiento y el art\\u00edculo, examinar\\u00e1n el manuscrito rigurosamente de acuerdo con su especialidad y los criterios de publicaci\\u00f3n de <strong>Fig\\u016bras<\\/strong> para posteriormente enviar el dictamen con la recomendaci\\u00f3n para su publicaci\\u00f3n (con las sugerencias de los cambios pertinentes) o la conveniencia de no publicarlo.<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Open Peer Review (OPR)","es_ES":"Revisi\\u00f3n por pares (open peer review, OPR)"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"185","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"36","parentId":"33","seq":"10"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"37","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"manualdereferencias","content":{"en_US":"<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">References according to <a style=\\"color: #1155cc;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.chicagomanualofstyle.org\\/home.html\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\">The Chicago Manual of Style 17th Edition<\\/a> <\\/span><\\/span>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">Formats are divided into:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">Author-date. It is used to cite the author in parenthesis. The complete information is written in the references. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">Notes and bibliography. It is used to refer specific notes in the text and footnotes. <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">Data is found complete in the bibliography. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">It is preferable to add the DOI for online books and articles. Nonetheless, when this information is unknown, the URL can be used instead. <\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">In order to avoid any difficulty in its retrieval, it was decided to omit the period after the URL (and DOI) in all references. This exception will apply for the digital and PDF versions of the article. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">a) Journal articles<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">b) Online articles<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">c) Books<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">c1) <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><em>Printed<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">c2) <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><em>Online<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">c3) <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><em>eBook<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">d) Websites<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">e) Audiovisual and other multimedia (recordings, app content, songs, albums, videos, audiobooks, TV Series, podcasts, etc. including online resources)<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">f)<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><em> Blogs<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">g) Magazines or newspapers<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1.27cm; text-indent: -1.27cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><a name=\\"_GoBack\\"><\\/a> <span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">h) Artworks<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1.25cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">h1) <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><em>Paintings, photographs, sculptures, or other works of art<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1.25cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">h2) <\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><em>Tables and figures<\\/em><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 1.25cm; text-indent: -1.25cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">i) Social media content<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><a href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/References_FINAL.pdf\\" download=\\"Reference Manual of Fig\\u016bras\\"><img src=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/iconoPDF.jpg\\"><\\/a><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">Las referencias de los art\\u00edculos se elaborar\\u00e1n de acuerdo a <\\/span><a style=\\"color: #1155cc;\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.chicagomanualofstyle.org\\/home.html\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\">The Chicago Manual of Style 17th Edition<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">El formato est\\u00e1 dividido en:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">1. Autor-fecha. Se ocupa para citar al autor mediante par\\u00e9ntesis. Los datos de la cita se ampl\\u00edan en las referencias. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\" align=\\"justify\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">2. Notas y bibliograf\\u00eda. Se emplea para llamadas en el texto y notas al pie de p\\u00e1gina. Los datos se completan en la bibliograf\\u00eda. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">Se preferir\\u00e1 ocupar el DOI para los libros y art\\u00edculos en l\\u00ednea; en caso de no contar con \\u00e9l, se pondr\\u00e1 el URL.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">Se decidi\\u00f3 que no se pondr\\u00e1 punto al final de direcciones electr\\u00f3nicas (tanto DOI como URL) en las referencias para que no se vea imposibilitada su consulta; esta excepci\\u00f3n se ocupar\\u00e1 para la versi\\u00f3n digital y PDF de los art\\u00edculos.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">a) Art\\u00edculos de revistas acad\\u00e9micas<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">b) Art\\u00edculos en l\\u00ednea<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">c) Libros<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-indent: 1.27cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">c1) <\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><em>Impresos<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-indent: 1.27cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">c2) <\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><em>En l\\u00ednea<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-indent: 1.27cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">c3<\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">) <\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><em>E-book<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">d) Websites<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">e) Recursos audiovisuales y multimedia (grabaciones, contenido digital, canciones, videos, CD, audiolibros, series de televisi\\u00f3n, pel\\u00edculas, podcasts, etc., incluyendo contenido en l\\u00ednea) <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">f) Blogs<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">g) Revistas y peri\\u00f3dicos<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">h) Ilustraciones<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 0.75cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><em><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">h1) Pinturas, fotograf\\u00edas, esculturas y otras piezas de arte<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 0.75cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><em><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">h2) Tablas y figuras<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 0.75cm; text-indent: -0.64cm; margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 115%;\\"><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">i) Redes sociales<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/Referencias_FINAL.pdf\\" rel=\\"noopener\\" download=\\"Manual de Referencias de Fig\\u016bras\\"> PDF<\\/a><\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Reference Manual of  Fig\\u016bras","es_ES":"Manual de Referencias de Fig\\u016bras"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"186","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"37","parentId":"33","seq":"11"},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},{"navigationMenuItem":{"navigationMenuItems":[],"_isDisplayed":true,"_isChildVisible":false,"_data":{"id":"38","contextId":"1","url":"","type":"NMI_TYPE_CUSTOM","path":"politicaseticasdepublicacion","content":{"en_US":"<p><strong>Code of Ethics<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">In order to submit a manuscript, it is necessary for each author to carefully read the Code of Ethics, and send it signed in a PDF file. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><em>Code of Ethics<\\/em><br><br><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/CodeEthics_15ene2019.pdf\\" download=\\"Code of Ethics\\">PDF<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><strong>Privacy Statement<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-top: 0.39cm; margin-bottom: 0.39cm; line-height: 150%; background: #ffffff;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">All information provided to <\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal <\\/strong><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\">will be exclusively used for the established purposes, and will not be given to third parties for its use with any other intentions.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-top: 0.39cm; margin-bottom: 0.39cm; line-height: 150%; background: #ffffff;\\"><strong><span lang=\\"en-US\\">Copyright<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">Texts published in <\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><strong> Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal <\\/strong><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\">are subject to the following<\\/span> <span lang=\\"en-US\\">regulations: <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">1. Authors retain the copyright and grant, <\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\">non-exclusively, the exploitation rights of accepted works for its publication in <\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research Academic Journal, <\\/strong><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\">giving to the journal the guarantee of being the first one to publish such work. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">2. All manuscripts are published exclusively online under a <\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><a style=\\"color: #1155cc;\\" href=\\"https:\\/\\/creativecommons.org\\/licenses\\/by-nc\\/4.0\\/deed.es\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\"><u>Creative Commons license of the type Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (by-nc)<\\/u><\\/a><\\/span>.<span lang=\\"en-US\\"> In this way, articles can be publicly copied, used, disseminated, transmitted and exposed, provided that: <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">a. The manuscript\\u2019s authorship and the original source of its publication are mentioned (journal\\u2019s editor and URL of the document).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">b. It is a non-profit work. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><span lang=\\"en-US\\">c. The existence and characteristics of this license agreement are mentioned. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">3. Self-archive conditions. <span lang=\\"en-US\\">The electronic dissemination, by the authors, of the Preprint version of the article in prestigious repositories before its final publication is allowed, on condition that they refer to its publication in <\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Research <\\/strong><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\"><strong>Academic Journal<\\/strong><\\/span><span lang=\\"en-US\\">. This will contribute to the previous dissemination so as to encourage a broader scope among the academic community. <\\/span><\\/p>","es_ES":"<p><strong>C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Para proponer un trabajo de investigaci\\u00f3n, es necesario que cada autor lea detenidamente el C\\u00f3digo de \\u00c9tica y lo env\\u00ede firmado en PDF.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><em>C\\u00f3digo de \\u00e9tica<\\/em><br><br><a class=\\"obj_galley_link pdf\\" style=\\"color: #007ab2; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #007ab2; display: inline-block; padding: 0 1em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 28px; text-decoration: none;\\" href=\\"\\/ojs\\/public\\/journals\\/1\\/descargas\\/CodigoEtica_110119_FINAL.pdf\\" download=\\"C\\u00f3digo de \\u00c9tica\\">PDF<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\"><strong>Declaraci\\u00f3n de privacidad<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-top: 0.39cm; margin-bottom: 0.39cm; line-height: 150%; background: #ffffff;\\">Todos los datos proporcionados a <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n <\\/strong> se usar\\u00e1n exclusivamente para los fines declarados en ella y no se proporcionar\\u00e1n por ning\\u00fan motivo a terceros ni para su uso con otros fines.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-top: 0.39cm; margin-bottom: 0.39cm; line-height: 150%; background: #ffffff;\\"><strong>Aviso de derechos de autor<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">Los textos publicados en <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n <\\/strong>est\\u00e1n sujetos a lo siguiente:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; border: none; padding: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">1. <span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">Los autores conservan los derechos de <\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">autor y ceden de forma no exclusiva los derechos de explotaci\\u00f3n de los trabajos aceptados para su publicaci\\u00f3n en <\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\"><strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong><\\/span><span style=\\"color: #000000;\\">, garantizando a la revista el derecho a ser la primera en publicar dicho trabajo. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">2. Los trabajos se publican exclusivamente de manera electr\\u00f3nica bajo una licencia <a style=\\"color: #1155cc;\\" href=\\"https:\\/\\/creativecommons.org\\/licenses\\/by-nc\\/4.0\\/deed.es\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\"><u>Creative Commons Reconocimiento-NoComercial (by-nc)<\\/u><\\/a>. De esta manera, los trabajos se pueden copiar, usar, difundir, transmitir y exponer p\\u00fablicamente, siempre y cuando:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">a. Se mencione la autor\\u00eda del trabajo y la fuente original de su publicaci\\u00f3n (editor de revistas y la URL de la obra).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">b. No existan fines de lucro de por medio.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">c. Se mencione la existencia y caracter\\u00edsticas de este acuerdo de licencia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;\\">3. Condiciones de auto-archivo. Se permite que los autores difundan electr\\u00f3nicamente la versi\\u00f3n Preprint de sus trabajos en repositorios de reconocido prestigio antes de su publicaci\\u00f3n definitiva, haciendo referencia a su publicaci\\u00f3n en <strong>Fig\\u016bras: Revista acad\\u00e9mica de investigaci\\u00f3n<\\/strong>. De esta manera se favorece la difusi\\u00f3n previa para que exista un mayor alcance entre la comunidad acad\\u00e9mica.<\\/p>"},"title":{"en_US":"Publication ethics","es_ES":"Pol\\u00edticas \\u00e9ticas de publicaci\\u00f3n"}},"_hasLoadableAdapters":false,"_metadataExtractionAdapters":[],"_extractionAdaptersLoaded":false,"_metadataInjectionAdapters":[],"_injectionAdaptersLoaded":false},"children":[],"_data":{"id":"187","menuId":"3","menuItemId":"38","